  WhatsApp Messages      [=====---------]   3   3/5 free
  Email Messages         [====---------]   18   Unlimited
  SMS Messages           [=-----------]     4   4/5 free

  Legend: Bar color matches channel brand color
  WhatsApp/SMS bars show warning color when approaching limit

Section 3: Daily Trend (Mini Chart)
