10.3 FLUTTER IMPLEMENTATION
-----------------------------

Circular Progress Ring:
- `percent_indicator` package: Simple, lightweight circular/linear indicators
  - CircularPercentIndicator with custom colors, size, and center text
  - Built-in animation support
- Custom implementation: `CustomPainter` with `Canvas.drawArc()`
- Syncfusion `syncfusion_flutter_gauges` for advanced radial gauge

Linear Progress Bars:
- Material 3 `LinearProgressIndicator` for basic bars
- `percent_indicator` for labeled linear bars with percentage text
- Custom: Stack with two Container widgets for filled/unfilled portions

Color Logic:
  usage < 50%:  ColorScheme.primary (brand purple)
  usage 50-80%: Color(0xFFFFA726)  (warning amber)
  usage > 80%:  ColorScheme.error   (Material red)
  usage = 100%: ColorScheme.error + "Limit reached" label

Sparkline Chart:
- `fl_chart` package for line charts (most popular Flutter chart library)
- `sparkline` package for minimal sparkline widgets
- Custom: `CustomPainter` drawing path from data points

Data Refresh:
- Pull-to-refresh on usage screen
- Background sync every 15 minutes via WorkManager
- Optimistic UI: Update count immediately on notification send


