SECTION 12: MATERIAL 3 COMPONENT RECOMMENDATIONS
================================================================================

12.1 SETTINGS PAGE COMPONENTS
-------------------------------

For building the notification settings screens, use these M3 components:

LISTTILE:
- Primary component for settings rows
- Supports leading icon, title, subtitle, trailing widget
- M3 specs: m3.material.io/components/lists/specs
- Use for: Channel list items, preference rows, info displays
- Theming: Inherits from ListTileThemeData

SWITCHLISTTILE:
- ListTile + Switch combination widget
- Perfect for: Feature toggles, channel on/off, DND toggles
- controlAffinity: Switch position (leading or trailing)
- Dense mode: For compact settings lists
- States: Active (primary color) / Inactive (outline color)
- M3 Switch with thumb icon: Checkmark when ON, X when OFF

EXPANSIONTILE:
- Collapsible section with arrow indicator
- Use for: Category-level preferences that expand to show channel toggles
- Animated icon and text color transitions between states
- Good for: Grouping related settings without navigation

CHIP:
- FilterChip: For day-of-week selectors in quiet hours
- ChoiceChip: For frequency selection (Immediate/Daily/Weekly)
- InputChip: For keyword notification triggers
- AssistChip: For quick actions (Test, Pause, Disconnect)

CARD:
- FilledCard: For connected channel cards
- OutlinedCard: For disconnected/available channel cards
- ElevatedCard: For the main usage summary card
- Use CardTheme for consistent elevation and shape

SWITCH:
- Material 3 Switch with optional icon (thumb icon)
- Track: colorScheme.primary when ON, outline when OFF
- Thumb: Can show checkmark when ON, X when OFF
- Size: 52x32dp default, expandable for accessibility

SLIDER:
- ContinuousSlider: For wait time between fallback attempts
- DiscreteSlider: For notification frequency (with tick marks)
- Use SliderThemeData for custom track/thumb colors

BOTTOM SHEET:
- ModalBottomSheet: For upgrade prompts and quick settings
- DraggableScrollableSheet: For long content (plan comparison)
- showModalBottomSheet with isScrollControlled: true for full expansion

SEGMENTED BUTTON:
- For binary/ternary choices: Sequential/Smart delivery mode
- For category view switcher: Category-first / Channel-first
- M3 replacement for ToggleButtons

NAVIGATION:
- NavigationBar (bottom): For main app navigation
- NavigationRail: For tablet/desktop notification hub
- Breadcrumbs: Custom widget for deep settings navigation

TIME PICKER:
- showTimePicker: For quiet hours start/end times
- M3 time picker with dial and input modes
- 12-hour or 24-hour format based on locale


