================================================================================
SECTION 13: LIGHT & DARK THEME ADAPTATION GUIDE
================================================================================

13.1 GENERAL PRINCIPLES
-------------------------

Material 3 Dynamic Color:
- Use ColorScheme.fromSeed() with brand seed color (midnight purple)
- Generates harmonious light AND dark schemes automatically
- On Android 12+: DynamicColorBuilder pulls from wallpaper
- Override key colors while keeping M3 harmony:
  - primary: Midnight purple (#2E1A47)
  - secondary: Gold accent (#FFD700)
  - tertiary: Teal for success states (#26A69A)

Theme Switching:
- ThemeMode.system: Auto-adapt to device setting (default)
- ThemeMode.light / ThemeMode.dark: User override
- Persist preference via SharedPreferences
- Respect HighContrast mode via MediaQuery.highContrastOf(context)


13.2 LIGHT THEME SPECIFICS
----------------------------

Background & Surface:
- Surface: Pure white (#FFFFFF) or near-white (#FAFAFA)
- Surface Container: Light gray (#F5F5F5) for cards
- Surface Container High: Slightly darker for elevated cards
- On Surface: Dark gray (#1C1B1F) for primary text
- On Surface Variant: Medium gray (#49454F) for secondary text

Channel Cards:
- Connected: Surface Container with left border in channel brand color
- Disconnected: Outlined card, no fill, muted icon
- Error: Surface Container with warning orange left border
- Hover/Press: Surface Container High

Status Dots (Light):
- Green: #2E7D32 (darker green for contrast on light bg)
- Amber: #E65100 (darker amber)
- Red: #C62828 (darker red)
- Gray: #757575 (medium gray)

Pro Badge (Light):
- Background: Purple-900 (#1A0033) or gradient purple-to-gold
- Text: White (#FFFFFF)
- Shadow: Subtle purple glow

Progress Bars (Light):
- Track: Surface Container Highest (#E6E1E5)
- Fill: Primary color with appropriate state color
- Text: On Surface

Toggle/Switch (Light):
- Track ON: Primary (#2E1A47)
- Track OFF: Surface Container Highest with outline
- Thumb ON: On Primary (white)
- Thumb OFF: Outline color


13.3 DARK THEME SPECIFICS
---------------------------

Background & Surface:
- Surface: Dark gray (#1C1B1F) or near-black (#121212)
- Surface Container: Slightly lighter (#211F26) for cards
- Surface Container High: (#2B2930) for elevated cards
- On Surface: Near-white (#E6E1E5) for primary text
- On Surface Variant: Light gray (#CAC4D0) for secondary text

Channel Cards:
- Connected: Surface Container with left border in channel brand color (brighter)
- Disconnected: Outlined card, muted outline, dim icon
- Error: Surface Container with warning amber left border
- Premium glow: Subtle gold border glow for Pro features

Status Dots (Dark):
- Green: #66BB6A (lighter green for visibility on dark bg)
- Amber: #FFA726 (lighter amber)
- Red: #EF5350 (lighter red)
- Gray: #9E9E9E (lighter gray)

Pro Badge (Dark):
- Background: Gold-400 (#FFD54F) or gradient gold-to-purple
- Text: Black (#000000)
- Glow: Subtle gold ambient glow

Progress Bars (Dark):
- Track: Surface Container Highest (#36343B)
- Fill: Primary color (lighter variant for dark theme)
- Text: On Surface

Toggle/Switch (Dark):
- Track ON: Primary (lighter variant, e.g., #9C27B0)
- Track OFF: Surface Container Highest with outline
- Thumb ON: On Primary
- Thumb OFF: Outline color

QR Code (Dark):
- QR modules: White on dark surface (inverted from light theme)
- QR background: Dark surface color
- Ensure sufficient contrast ratio (>4.5:1)


13.4 CHANNEL-SPECIFIC BRAND COLORS
-------------------------------------

Each channel has a brand color that should be used consistently:

WhatsApp:
  Light theme: #128C7E (dark teal)
  Dark theme:  #25D366 (bright green)

Telegram:
  Light theme: #0077B6 (dark blue)
  Dark theme:  #34AADC (light blue)

Email:
  Light theme: #D93025 (Gmail red)
  Dark theme:  #EA4335 (lighter Gmail red)

SMS:
  Light theme: #1565C0 (dark blue)
  Dark theme:  #42A5F5 (light blue)

Instagram:
  Light theme: #E1306C (brand pink)
  Dark theme:  #E4405F (lighter pink)

Discord:
  Light theme: #5865F2 (brand purple)
  Dark theme:  #7289DA (lighter purple)

Slack:
  Light theme: #4A154B (brand aubergine)
  Dark theme:  #6B2C6C (lighter aubergine)

Push (UNJYNX brand):
  Light theme: #2E1A47 (midnight purple)
  Dark theme:  #9C27B0 (lighter purple)


13.5 ACCESSIBILITY COLOR CONSIDERATIONS
-----------------------------------------

- Never rely on color alone to convey status (always pair with icon/shape/text)
- Minimum contrast ratios per WCAG 2.1 AA:
  - Normal text (< 18sp): 4.5:1 against background
  - Large text (>= 18sp or >= 14sp bold): 3:1 against background
  - UI components and graphical objects: 3:1 against adjacent colors
- Test with color blindness simulators:
  - Protanopia (red-blind): Green vs Red dots may look similar
  - Solution: Use different shapes (circle vs triangle vs square)
- High contrast mode: Increase all borders to 2dp, increase dot size to 12dp
- Dynamic type: Support text scaling up to 200% without layout breaking


